<small class="LGrav"><img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=8af353bc52e0c3c2873e7e65b578d07a&amp;rating=X&amp;size=27&amp;default=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.sallarp.com%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fdilectio%2Fimages%2FAvatarReplace.png" alt="" />
